INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('607', '1', '2016-10-22 07:32:06', '2016-10-22 07:32:06', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>CEO Message</strong></span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The future of the travel industry worldwide is bright and is being projected as the key economic driver in many regions, driven by competition, new business investments and an increase in consumer confidence and spending.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">As a well-established and progressive travel company operating in KSA-with equal strengths in outbound travel  Jawlat travel and tourism is well equipped to take on the many challenges and the involving dynamics of the industry.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">we have harnessed our intrinsic market knowledge and business acumen to expand the company by way of both organic growth and new area of business. we continue to identify opportunities,</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Invest in services and introduce technology to stay abreast of regional and global trends, and offer the very best to our clients, partners and employees, we have been the pioneers in this aspect of business since inception and have built up an enviable reputation in the market for our expertise and access, we also believe that in this buoyant travel environment, the focus is on you.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I join my team in assuring you of fulfilling all your travel experiences come, explore the world with us</p>\r\n\r\n<h6 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mr. Wael Khaled Fahad Al Boayz (CEO)</h6>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000080;\"><strong>Founded in 2016</strong></span></h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">JAWLAT is one of the newest and promising company for travel and tourism in KSA, has offering adverse range of outstanding travel, tourism services on everything from a simple flights booking, holidays packages and related requirements to every corners of the globe.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jawlat uses its vast resources to provide innovation and cost effective travel solutions to business and leisure travelers to all parts of the world. Our expertise in sourcing, planning and implementation providers a hassle free holiday or business trip anywhere in the world.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">Advantages</span> </strong></h1>\r\n<strong>Trust:</strong> quality service provided by professional and client-oriented staff\r\n\r\n<strong>Comfort:</strong> we take care of all other travel related issues\r\n\r\n<strong>Prompt reply:</strong> all customer requests are efficiently answered\r\n\r\n<strong>Save time and effort:</strong> multiple offers and different customizable options\r\n\r\n<strong>Save money:</strong> our negotiating power with various suppliers and providers reflects our pricing.\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">Core Activities</span></strong></h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Corporate services</li>\r\n 	<li>Jawlat Travel service</li>\r\n 	<li>Jawlat holidays\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Corporate service</span> </strong></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nJawlat travel and tourism delivers cost effective travel solutions to many of the KSAS Leading organizations. We are known for our personalized partnerships, flexible approach to corporate travel management, and our ability to tailor programs to our clients needs.\r\n\r\nWe offer\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Travel support 24/7</li>\r\n 	<li>Saving on both money and time</li>\r\n 	<li>Experienced corporate travel managers</li>\r\n 	<li>Flexibility with a wide choice of travel options low cost, best route, best value</li>\r\n 	<li>Exceptional service and efficiency</li>\r\n 	<li>Detailed invoices and itineraries</li>\r\n 	<li>Detailed management information systems reports</li>\r\n 	<li>We provide comprehensive business travel management services to\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Multinational companies</li>\r\n 	<li>Small and medium businesses</li>\r\n 	<li>Government organizations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Jawlat Travel Services</strong></span></h3>\r\nJawlat Travel and Tourism covers all aspects of travels. According to the need of our valued client our Travel Packages includes from pre-designed &amp; scheduled tourism packages to custom packages, cosmetic therapies to medical surgeries and short language &amp; academia courses to degree programs in variety of destinations.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Private city guide city tours.</li>\r\n 	<li>Restaurant reservations</li>\r\n 	<li>Passport visa service</li>\r\n 	<li>Umrah services</li>\r\n 	<li>English language courses</li>\r\n 	<li>Cruises</li>\r\n 	<li>Hotels booking</li>\r\n 	<li>Apartment and villas booking</li>\r\n 	<li>Euro raid tickets</li>\r\n 	<li>Private jet</li>\r\n 	<li>Charter flights</li>\r\n 	<li>Camping</li>\r\n 	<li>European league tickets</li>\r\n 	<li>Family packages</li>\r\n 	<li>Cosmetic therapy</li>\r\n 	<li>Hair transplant surgery</li>\r\n 	<li>Shopping packages</li>\r\n 	<li>Antitoxins from the body</li>\r\n 	<li>Physio therapy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Jawlat holidays</strong></span></h3>\r\nWe are a one stop- shop for all of your travel needs across the globe. We take care of your hotel reservations, car rentals (self-driven or with chauffeur), offering Tailor made itineraries ranging from luxury to budget, charter tour packages, cruises, trains, coach tours, adventure tours, honeymoon packages, student travel, group travel MICE and more. We are renowned for having the most economical and competitive travel deals. Jawlat holidays can help with all dimensions of your travel planning. No matter where you plan to go, we can help you get there at a great price.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About Jawlat', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '360-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-22 07:32:06', '2016-10-22 07:32:06', '', '360', 'http://localhost/jawlat-dev/360-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
